{"tid":149330,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【秋官開騷撞咗期】無緣父女擋上陣 鄭欣宜諗計撐老竇","createTime":"2017-03-09T08:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T21:58:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74582c67823b3d5ed0d762e0f61c393054724582","tid":149330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T08:20:56.000Z","msg":"錢小豪、林明禎、蔡瀚億(Babyjohn)、鄭欣宜、詹瑞文、趙學而、邵音音等，噚晚喺尖沙嘴出席電影《救殭清道夫》首映禮，現場安排咗啲小朋友扮殭屍仔。<br />\n<br />\n講到爹哋鄭少秋就嚟開演唱會，欣宜話：「之前老竇有叫我做嘉賓，但嗰時我唔喺香港，出埠半工半放假，我唔係唔撐老豆，除咗去現場都仲可以諗其他方法盡量去支持，例如拍片咁，或者等佢慶祝入行60周年，再開演唱會時，再去撐佢場。」(新聞連結：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2lG41NP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lG41NP&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9otU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=87ed7728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2lG41NP</a>)<br />\n大馬女神林明禎第一次拍電影，兼喺香港出席首映禮，估唔到會着得咁實密，錢小豪即刻搶答話：「林明禎個外貌已經夠晒性感，今次同女神合作，可惜冇乜艷福，Babyjohn同佢就多啲對手戲，我只係對殭屍，今次讓咗比Babyjohn。」小豪似乎好搭糖，佢繼續大力讚林明禎：「佢眼神已經係美女殭屍，冇對白都做得好好，又好乖，吊威也時要兼顧個靚樣，一心二用，又勤力，唔使埋位都喺側邊睇住我哋拍戲。」<br />\n林明禎就話自己細細個已經睇錢小豪嘅電影，今次第一次拍戲就愛上拍電影，雖然戲中扮殭屍，唔使講對白，但見到自己扮殭屍都覺得好恐佈，心情好緊張。佢仲話：「這次要不斷被殺，希望下一次可以我去殺人。」Babyjohn就話同女神合作，半個鐘已經混熟咗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170309/large/1489039948_5be8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170309%2Flarge%2F1489039948_5be8.jpg&h=d94c1c25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170309/56404539\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170309%2F56404539&d=0fhT0ZiErqSmjIt08Df9otU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6ccb30f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170309%2F56404539&h=3ce78496\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170309/56404539</a>"},{"pid":"e2afef8ba4c1a9516c8bd5e4373fe7e96ac9686e","tid":149330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:21:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"746bd8a858b95694e595962b581ed178caa26f37","tid":149330,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T10:39:06.000Z","msg":"會唔會有人真金白銀入場睇欣宜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c441c81e39552445c9f29c2ca3358b09141fccea","tid":149330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T13:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e923d0d1b4b5445a862f2afd7f1a34562089e6a6","tid":149330,"uid":9188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:22:34.000Z","msg":"千其唔好黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我老豆老母係想睇秋官唔係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be72e1f61cb299004e24927e85e59839243c7efa","tid":149330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T18:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec11908749c0fc2ec791562ba0bf85450676b39a","tid":149330,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T20:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0c5dd177973fb3f78eabbed3b740886f2733bd","tid":149330,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T21:58:07.000Z","msg":"唔準提老母.jpg"}]}